            li Users earn
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png") 
              | by taking incentivized API calls
            li cApps are the first design space for
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
                
        div.list
          div.head
            b In-App Payments
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-bag.png")
          ul
            li Powers in-app, fee-less payments with
