        div.list
          div.head
            b Smart Contracts
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-contract.png", style="width: 19px;")
          ul
            li Native protocol support for smart contracts
            li Smart contract client libraries in different languages
            li Smart contracts pave the way for
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
              | to move into the cash register
        
