      div.roadmap-lists 
        div.list
          div.head
            b Ready for Cash Registers
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-cash-reg.png")
          ul
             li Using smart contracts, Storecoin can solve for Chargebacks
             li Merchants wanting to accept zero-fee payments would stake a small percentage of inventory to insure against potential chargebacks
             li Decentralized Service Agents – sAgents – review and reach consensus on all Chargeback cases. A smart contract then executes         
               
        div.list
          div.head
            b Payment Fraud Supported
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-shield.png")
          ul
             li Users stake tokens to file fraud tickets
             li sAgents review fraud tickets from customers
             li If approved, the fraud is reviewed by the non-profit (the non-profit makes a final determination on early fraud cases)
             li Fraud refunds are paid for by the Storecoin Security Fund and/or by equally using the stake of all dWorkers
             li If payment fraud grows, dWorkers and the non-profit are both equally incentivized to fix fraud through Governance
             li Governance will likely reach consensus on new features and monetary policy to reduce future fraud
              
        div.list
          div.head
            b Global KYC/AML Compliance
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-law.png")
          ul
            li KYC and AML checks are compliant with the laws and national security demands of 190+ countries; this logic is hard coded into all decentralized worker nodes
            li If the laws of country X prevent transactions from being processed by decentralized nodes in country Y, the Storecoin protocol will support this natively, on chain
            li A long-term, security-first approach to building globally compliant infrastructure for zero-fee, p2p payments will give Storecoin developers the best opportunity to be embedded into banking and financial infrastructure around the globe.
        
        div.column-head 
          b $STORE AS GLOBAL CURRENCY
